title: TOP 5 DOBLAJES JAPONESES QUE TE DEJARAN LOS PELOS DE PUNTA
tags: luchosbacks|doblajes|top|seiyus|actores de voz|de japon|mejores
description: Chicos, sin saberlo, desde muy pequeños hemos estado influenciados por la cultura japonesa. Y es que, gran parte de las producciones de animación que disfrutamos en su momento y que seguimos consumiendo hoy en día, son producidas en ese país oriental. Estas producciones son conocidas mundialmente como animes, un estilo único de dibujo plasmado primariamente en los mangas, y que luego cobran vida gracias a la tecnología de las distintas casas de animación en Japón. El proceso de darle vida a un comic o manga, no solo pasa por la calidad de los efectos especiales utilizados, pues una parte importantísima recae en los efectos de sonido y sobre todo en las voces de los personajes, pues esa recreación no se hace a través de un programa, para ello se necesitan actores de doblaje, conocidos en Japón como seiyuus. Estas personas son las encargadas de transmitir a través de su voz, todo tipo de emociones, a cada uno de los personajes que vemos en pantallas; un trabajo no es tan fácil como uno puede pensar. Hoy veremos casos de interpretaciones de seiyuus que nos dejarán totalmente asombrados, y que nos harán pensar, que es mucho mejor ver un anime en su idioma original. Así que…. ¿Estás listos para ver a qué nivel llega el doblaje japonés en el mundo del anime? ¿No? No me importa. Allá vamos. TOP 5 DOBLAJES JAPONESES QUE TE DEJARAN LOS PELOS DE PUNTA.

title: Black Clover - Opening 13 BREAKDOWN
tags: black clover op 13|Grandeur|the dark triad|timeskip black clover|asta|black clover opening 13|crunchyroll|black clover|anime opening|anime op|anime opening analysis|anime op breakdown|asta devil|asta’s mother|asta’s mom|zenon|yuno vs zenon|yami vs Dante|Noelle vs vanica|Noelle|valkyrie armor|mermaid armour|snow man|ブラッククローバー|anime trailer|anime|bc|bc op 13|bc op 1
description: This video explains Black Clover’s OP 13, which is being used for the Spade Kingdom Arc! OP 13 had a lot of imagery that gives callbacks to both previous OPs and the Black Clover manga. OP 13 features the song ‘Grandeur’ by Snowman.Join this channel to get access to perks and emotes:https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChp-A9cwI6zVcDEuIXO71kQ/joinOTHER VIDEOS:What If Black Clover characters had QUIRKS? - https://youtu.be/Xwc2HPmWMwcYuno's TRAGIC BACKSTORY - https://youtu.be/4wHmXcTObaUBlack Clover OP 13: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aaZq6SXXNt4Art:Asta’s devil + Asta’s mother: https://twitter.com/iluvluvnutellaZeno smiling fanart: https://www.deviantart.com/alanfanartsdh/art/Black-clover-Zenon-VS-Yuno-828742605Lucifero colouring: https://www.reddit.com/r/BlackClover/comments/fjog89/chapter_234_lucifero/Tags:ZenonBlack Clover Op 13BC OP 13black clover opening 13Grandeur Snow ManDark TriadVideo Information:This video breaks down opening 13 for black clover. OP 13 had a J-pop song called ‘Grandeur’ (by Snowman) which worked really well when paired with the openings visuals.The OP begins with Asta walking through a red hallway with candles surrounding him; this shade of red is the same colour we see when Asta’s devil usually appears. The  only occasion in the manga where candles were on the ground surrounding Asta like this, was when he was about to perform a devil binding ritual, to properly gain control over his anti-magic abilities. This opening scene is a reference to that devil-binding ritual and therefore it makes sense that the red aura of his devil should be illuminating the shot. Additionally, this opening moment is also mirroring black clover’s OP 1, where we saw a younger Asta walking in the same way, before the scene pauses on his face and has a black and white effect. The same effect can be seen in opening 13 and this intentional parallel is meant to show us how much he’s grown between OP and OP 13.Opening 13 then moves on to Asta flying through the sky on his demon slayer sword, as Finral watches in amazement from the ground. This is a throwback to chapter 232, when Finral couldn’t help but admire Astra’s progress from someone who had no magic and couldn’t even fly on a broom to what he is today.We then get a few cool character shots featuring those who were training in the heart kingdom, such as Luck, Leopold, Noelle, Secre and Mimosa. The scene then switches over to Yuno, who stands on top of the golden dawn staircase. We’ve seen in the past how usually only the captain or vice captain of the golden dawn stands atop that staircase and during the filler Yuno was promoted to vice captain.After this there’s a brief shot of this mysterious woman. This moment is a flashback to the past in which Asta’s mother is about to die, and it’s immediately followed by a 1 second clip of a devil possessed Asta going berserk. This scene is interspersed with a glimpse of Yuno’s mother and a flashback image of Zenon from the dark triad, during the night they killed the spade kingdom royal family. We briefly see a present day Yuno screaming in anguish, which was a scene directly from the manga after the golden dawn was just totally wrecked by Zenon.Speaking of the dark triad, they appear immediately after this and it was really interesting to note Zenon’s facial expression here, as he genuinely appears shocked by something. Lucifero then got his own individual moment in this opening because based on everything we know so far he is the strongest devil and the true villain of this arc. Asta is then seen fighting against some nameless spade kingdom goons, before the opening gives us the real thing we’ve been waiting for, which is a preview of the three main fights from the beginning of this arc. Yuno vs zenon looks like it’s gonna be great, Noelle vs Vanica also got some screen time and for Yami vs Dante, we saw Yami in the position to do his death thrust spell.As the opening comes to a close we get a look at the tree of qlipoth which will connect the underworld to the human world and allow the devils to cross over, if the dark triad succeed in their plan.We see the heart kingdom queen falling down in the same manner as in the cover of volume 26, before our boy Nacht makes an appearance.

title: Ein Machinima aufnehmen ist schwieriger, als wir dachten...
tags: game two|gametwo|machinima|game two 2021|game two machinima|game two 188|game two outtakes|machinima deutsch|machinima german|machinima game|machinima games|machinima geschichte|machinima outtakes
description: Machinimas sind Filme, die man komplett innerhalb eines Videospiels aufnimmt. Eigentlich eine coole Sache: Sich ne coole Story überlegen, online treffen und mit den Tools, die einem das entsprechende Spiel bietet das bestmögliche Ergebnis erzielen. Dumm nur, wenn man sich Dinge vorgenommen hat, die sich letztendlich gar nicht so einfach umsetzen lassen, man von KI- oder zufallsbedingten Ereignissen abhängig ist oder einem das Spiel einfach einen Strich durch die Rechnung macht. Und zu guter Letzt kommt natürlich auch noch die eigene Dummheit dazu. Es gibt viele Fallstricke auf dem Weg zum Ingame-Film. In diesem Video haben wir versucht, den Struggle bestmöglich abzubilden... channel_desc: Bei Game Two zeigen wir unsere Liebe zu Videospielen auf charmant bescheuerte Art und Weise: Aktuelle Game-Reviews, Gaming-News, viel Humor und eine ordentliche Prise Hauen & Pappe – egal ob für Vollblut-Gamer, Gelegenheits-Zocker oder Noobs. Game Two ist Gaming-Show, Informationen aus dem Gaming-Kosmos & Comedy. Verpackt in drei unterhaltsame Videos pro Woche. Sei dabei, wenn wir Games testen, Games-News mit euch diskutieren und uns mal wieder nicht ganz so ernst nehmen.Wir, das sind die Rocket Beans. Unabhängig von PC-Master-Race, PlayStation, Xbox oder Switch – in der deutschen Gaming-Szene kommt man um die Bohnen nicht herum. Sofia, Lara Loft, Simon, Budi, Etienne und Nils erwarten euch mit einem Gaming-Erlebnis der etwas anderen Art. channel_desc: 【English Biography】Vicke Blanka is a versatile songwriter/composer.His songs are best characterized by his individuality, good melody’s and his beautiful falsetto voice.He started composing music when he was only in elementary school.With the aim to pursue music as a career, he decided to attend university in Tokyo.In 2016, he was finally able to debut. Since his debut, his performances have impressed the audience, making.【Japanese Biography】2018年2ndアルバム「wizard」収録曲「まっしろ」がドラマの挿入歌に抜擢され、ハイライトシーンを飾るバラード曲として話題を呼ぶ。翌年、サブスクリプション音楽サービスSpotifyのTV CM曲として発表された3rdシングル「Ca Va?」は、その中毒性ある楽曲とワードセンスが各方面から評価。多才ぶりを見せつけた圧倒的な作品づくりと、LIVEパフォーマンスは、オリジナリティを驀進する存在に。同年10月から、FM802「MUSIC FREAKS」のレギュラーDJを隔週で担当。トーク力のスキルの高さを発揮。2020年8月19日(水)には4thシングル「ミラージュ」を発売予定。玉木宏主演のカンテレ・フジテレビ系ドラマ「竜の道 二つの顔の復讐者」オープニング曲「ミラージュ」、矢作穂香×伊藤健太郎W主演のドラマ特区「ピーナッツバターサンドウィッチ」オープニング主題歌「Shekebon!」他、全5曲を収録予定。「Zoff」サングラスコレクションのビジュアルモデルに起用、Twitchの公式パートナーに認定され「FORTNITE」のプロゲーマーとしてストリーム配信するなど音楽以外の分野での活躍も展開。
